metadata.name: Borderline
metadata.description:
This work was created to capture about less energy of a dancer. He felt that he was at the lowest point of his life. His body had to keep moving until the end of the song. He didn't want anything and didn't want to communicate with anyone.

 For those who purchase this work will get giveaway NFTs Music for this video.

1/1 edition
Dimensions: 1920 × 1080
